      nunc. Nullam nec purus nec nunc consectetur ultricies. Donec nec nunc consectetur,
      ultricies nunc nec, ultricies nunc. Nullam nec purus nec nunc consectetur ultricies.
    </text>
  </view>
</bottom-sheet:bottom-sheet>
